beer.beer_description:
Produced from a selection of the world’s highest quality malted barley including specialty crystal malts from Belgium & Germany. Combined with classically Noble German Hops & a beautiful Belgian yeast strain that brings all the ingredients together. A brilliant dark ruby coloured Belgian styled pale ale. Aromatics are classic Belgian that follow through in the flavour. A sweet front palate from the rich crystal malts, with hop bitterness to balance creating a drying mid palate to a finish that leaves you begging for another.
Food pairing – Great with meats & rich deserts.
